Title: Angel Face Botanicals Super Detox - Organic Deep Pore Facial Cleanser Face Wash(145.5 ml)
Description:
Super Detox Deep Pore Facial Cleanser is enriched with botanicals, essential oils, vitamins, replenishing oil, and activated charcoal to gently and clean and nourish your skin. 
 
Super Detox Cleanser is made with mild & effective cleansing agents to deeply clean your pores of toxins & bacteria for smooth clear skin. Our unique clarifying formula acts like a magnet to remove dirt and oils below the surface of your skin, gently purging toxins out of your pores. 
 
An oil-controlling, replenishing blend of Essential Oils consisting of Rose Geranium, Rosemary, Lavender, Lemon, Lime, and Orange works to balance your skin for a clear, bright complexion. 
 
Astringent, Antiseptic and Regenerative, this cleanser is fortified with Antioxidants: Lichen, Black Willow Bark, Aloe Vera, Green, White, and Rooibos Teas; plus Vitamins: B-complex, C Ester, and E. 
 
Details: 
Activated Charcoal is amazingly absorbent, known to effectively cleanse the skin, unclog pores, remove deeper impurities and dead skin cells, resulting in smooth, supple skin. One teaspoon of activated charcoal has a surface area of more than a football field. Dirt, toxins, heavy metals, chemicals & other poisons are attracted to the charcoal molecules and washed away. The beauty of Activated Charcoal is that it removes these nasties without adsorbing vitamins and nutrients, leaving your skin radiantly healthy. 
MSM is a natural sulfur compound that is anti-inflammatory and anti-microbial. MSM feeds the formation of collagen and elastin and discourages the formation of wrinkles and scar tissue. 
DMAE and Hyaluronic Acid: beneficial for cellular hydration, reducing the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles. 
Cocoamidopropyl Betaine and Decyl Glucoside are mild, vegetable sudsing agents. 
 
4.85 oz in a plastic bottle with twist spout cap. Also available on Amazon in 2.35 oz and 8.9 oz bottles.
